snippet.title: Best VGM 2402 - Metal Masters - Metal Beat (Intro)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GameBoy
Metal Masters (1993)
Metal Beat (Intro)
Alberto Gonzalez (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkNWfN6O-L-hScpaHSJ6b1g)
